features.name: Visual Enchantments
features.description: Resource Pack that shows enchantments on items to better distinguish what enchantments are on them without reading their names

features.name: Brewing Guide
features.description: A resource pack that displays a brewing guide when inside a brewing stand GUI

features.name: OptiFine Texture Support
features.description: Adds CIT and CEM support to fabric so you can have custom item textures and custom entity models.

features.name: Inventory Hotswap
features.description: Hold ALT to quickly swap items from your inventory to your hotbar, or hold ALT + SHIFT to swap an entire inventory row with your hotbar.

features.name: Distinct Potions
features.description: A resource pack that makes all potions look different so you can tell them apart from each other without reading their names

features.name: Dynamic Lights
features.description: Torches and other items generate light around the player like in optifine

features.name: Performance Enhancements
features.description: Mods that increase your FPS in-game, including Lithium, Starlight, Sodium, Reese's Sodium Options, and Sodium Extra.

features.name: Minimalist Armor
features.description: Resource pack that edits armor to show your skin but still allows you to know what armor you're wearing

features.name: Shaders
features.description: Allows the use of Optifine Shaders through a mod called Iris Shaders.

features.name: Essential Mod
features.description: Adds friend list like on xbox and also adds cosmetics/emotes. Also has cross-world messaging, and you can invite friends to your singleplayer worlds without hosting a server.

features.name: Minihud
features.description: Shows more detailed information for certain HUD elements

features.name: Physics
features.description: Adds physics to minecraft!

features.name: MiniMap
features.description: Xaero's Minimap mod

features.name: Advancement Plaques
features.description: Shows prettier advancement popups

features.name: Litematica
features.description: View schematics as a hologram in your world, and even auto-place blocks where they should go!

features.name: Visual Talismans
features.description: Brand new texture pack for Jacqueb's talismans datapack that will show a distinct icon for each talisman!

features.name: Chunks Fade In
features.description: Make chunks fade in

features.name: Ambient Sounds
features.description: Adds ambient sounds to minecraft, through a mod called Mambience

features.name: World Map
features.description: Xaero's World Map

features.name: Mod Menu
features.description: Adds a "Mods" button to your menu so you can see what you have installed
